ABOUT
Wallpaper Cycler is a free application made in Visual Basic 6 that can be used to change desktop background by cycling through different images in the folder specified by the user or automatically at every windows startup. It includes an intuitive beautiful user-interface that lets you easily manage the software and the desktop backgrounds.

DOWNLOAD
http://projects.robinrizvi.info/WCsetup.exe
 
